    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The majority of credibility factors have been assessed and the model demonstrates adequate performance for hemolysis prediction at MRL 3. Three factors (Model inputs, Test samples, Equivalency of input parameters) remain not-assessed, but the team judges these gaps to be beyond the current scope and unlikely to materially affect the overall credibility conclusion given the Monte Carlo UQ already performed. The package is accepted with a recommendation to address the unassessed factors in a subsequent assessment cycle.",
